Other Packages
javamoon.core Java Moon model.

 

Complete API to collect information from several languages with the aim of providing a common framework to refactor the code with certain language independence. The API allows to represents the main abstractions (MOON Metamodel) and its extensions using concrete language. More concretely, the Java extension is contained in the javamoon package.
